0.03649544,0.04179238,0.01619606,-0.01909980,-0.00555280,0.06836489,-0.03474334,-0.01790052,-0.01342904,0.08420923,-0.03534110,0.04262426,-0.06457905,-0.00114802,-0.03457574,0.03682460,-0.05690569,-0.09292526,0.02967829,-0.01741198,-0.01247003,0.06676032,-0.06983092,-0.03030075,0.02689283,-0.04492581,0.00438628,-0.02150846,-0.06396962,-0.04375376,0.00527386,0.00503180,0.01113089,-0.05893913,-0.04099739,-0.05933329,0.00554946,0.02181118,0.04961263,0.13274214,-0.02857240,0.02238761]',E'Redirection\n\n```elixir\ndefmodule HelloWeb.Router do\n  ...\n\n  scope "/", HelloWeb do\n    ...\n    get "/", PageController, :home\n    get "/redirect_test", PageController, :redirect_test\n    ...\n  end\nend\n```\n\nThen we''ll change `PageController`''s `home` action of our controller to do nothing but to redirect to our new route.\n\n```elixir\ndefmodule HelloWeb.PageController do\n  use HelloWeb, :controller\n\n  def home(conn, _params) do\n    redirect(conn, to: ~p"/redirect_test")\n  end\nend\n\n```','{"source": "phoenix", "version": "1.7", "language": "elixir", "title": "Controllers", "section_title": "controllers", "url": "https://github.com/phoenixframework/phoenix/blob/main/guides/controllers.md", "topics": "phoenix,elixir,controllers", "categories": "web,elixir,fullstack,realtime"}');
